Message: Hi, despite following the guidelines, our ad is getting rejected

Hi Nirmal, apologies for the delayed response. 

Looks like the reason for your rejects are because of the claims your ad is making on pricing. Recent case studies has shown that the minimal coverage for auto insurance is at least $29. 

Lower than that has not been achievable at the moment, therefore, we cannot allow ads promoting pricing such as yours, unless provided substantial evidence to back up that claim.

If you wish to run your ad, please update your creative to the correct pricing and we would be happy to review and approve. Thank you
